title: Porsche Cayman GT4 -- TEST/DRIVE
description: This season, The Drive brought 11 of today's best performance cars to Thunderhill Raceway Park in Willows, CA for a group test and quick reviews. With contributors A.J. Baime, Matt Farah, Mike Guy, Mike Spinelli and Lawrence Ulrich. This week, It's the delicious Porsche Cayman GT4.
